OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHolocaust survivor         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fconfronts Braverman over   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Flanguage                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The home secretary has said she will   
OL,6, not apologise for her language, after a
OL,7, Holocaust survivor criticised her for  
OL,8, describing migrants as an "invasion".  
OL,10,FJoan Salter, 83, confronted Suella     
OL,11,FBraverman during a meeting in her      
OL,12,FFareham constituency on Friday.        
OL,14,FShe said the home secretary's rhetoric 
OL,15,Freminded her of the language the Nazis 
OL,16,Fused to justify murdering her family.  
OL,18,FBut Ms Braverman said her language     
OL,19,Fdemonstrated the "scale of the problem"
OL,20,Fwith illegal migration.                
